{"tid":1630314,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[重點]幾個文宣方向!!!","createTime":"2019-10-06T12:04:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T05:03:49.000Z","uid":32731,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"3201de05201ba940d56a1217fe9992849f2ccdd9","tid":1630314,"uid":32731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:04:37.000Z","msg":"今個月既發展好快 但同時進步左好多 值得鼓勵 <br />\n但同時卧底做法層出不窮 包括以下<br />\n1. 黨鐵落閘 防暴駐守後放火<br />\n2.火魔燒中記者 (己知手足救火 並且係燃料滴出) <br />\n3.岩岩長沙灣燒公園<br />\n個人覺得係不能推斷我方無可能做出該事情 <br />\n係對我方係好不利 (如上述 第3<br />\n正如上次屯門水魔中左記者 之後民記劈頭向記者道歉 再表達對記者感激<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">所以今次火魔有救火片斷係好有用</span><br />\n<br />\n日後文宣方向<br />\n1.表明日後行動手法及宗旨 e.g 4色分類法   包括唔會破壞公園呢類休憩設施 脫離目標<br />\n2.解釋 助證手足唔會做出傷害無辜行為 (e.g 如手足向記者救火)<br />\n3.將日後有關脫離宗旨既行動指向黑狗<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n絕對支持手足行動 不過要對準暴政目標<br />\n第3點絕對不是割席,而是將黑狗一直以黎既暴力 卧底行為連繫<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">帶出黑狗絕對會做得出任何詆毀手足既行為 共產黨乜都會做得出!!!!</span>"},{"pid":"91c6b4f7debc0b38bc28502c635fb74f5b997b24","tid":1630314,"uid":130079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:07:57.000Z","msg":"［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630201\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630201</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現時連登急需亦好要一個<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">英文台/或者係新既英文介面，全部台都有英文版咁。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n主要用途係對外文宣用，如果個論壇冧左，<span style=\"color: purple;\">外國人更加清楚lihkg被攻擊同香港自由被剝既嚴重性</span>。<br />\n<br />\ntwitter有lihkg,reddit開post<br />\n但始終都唔係lihkg開英文台<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好處：<br />\n1.連登多左流覽量，廣告費多左<br />\n2.同上，每次被攻擊都睇到香港無自由，the world is watching<br />\n3.理論上少風向文宣，因為如果要落手帶風向，對家就要大學畢業既人，文宣戰立即少左散仔協會參戰，但香港市民最多就係呢一堆人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家如果見到既<br />\n幫手：<br />\n1.<span style=\"color: red;\">幫推，唔該3連推一次</span><br />\n2.連登search其他 英文台 國際台，<span style=\"color: green;\">將入面相關要求既post再推</span><br />\n<br />\n3.share link去fb tg，叫其他有account既人入黎再一齊做返1同2<br />\n4.<span style=\"color: orange;\">堅持每日全部post再一推</span><br />\n5.Fb 連登到留comment，叫連仔開英文台<br />\n6. Fb進行洗版式接龍活動，令到連仔開到/知道要開英文台為止<br />\n7.太舊既post只可以推番三個上水，幫手推埋thx<br />\n<br />\n如果你係要求開英文台post樓主既：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">集中連推自己所有既英文台post，我會幫推，唔好放棄推<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"f77ad32a1912b736aea82910858e87caf9f85f0f","tid":1630314,"uid":32731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:08:35.000Z","msg":"唔好唔記得當初我地稅務大樓既道歉係幾有用<br />\n即使今次係有救火片段 我都覺得要同記者講聲唔好意思<br />\n始終係我地失誤 我地唔可以橫蠻無忌"},{"pid":"f5332f6287f6c289e2b10bb124c703bb9c8ae1e9","tid":1630314,"uid":303304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:11:09.000Z","msg":"大家知唔知道宜家外國人點諗勇武<br />\n勇武要大家backup 啊！<br />\n<br />\n正式宣布：文宣洗地開始［行動po求置頂］<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630198\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630198</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f8338de5269f428a4750739ef24413f390a80a23","tid":1630314,"uid":313312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:12:03.000Z","msg":"邊個大大聲話集中<br />\n<br />\n鞭屍時間<br />\n<br />\n集中撚答到我問題，先好叫人出黎<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1628223\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1628223</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f01fad3ead454fb3b74edbe7aca9ce70682d9223","tid":1630314,"uid":32731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:12:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89ca4ad68990c2631def6a0536931cde70347f0e","tid":1630314,"uid":32731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:15:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"351d0c52c04e612263cff4f79d2343291dcdca85","tid":1630314,"uid":283080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:17:06.000Z","msg":"同埋而加交通封鎖既情況下去番自己區好Ｄ！<br />\n<br />\n最重要最重要係<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不被捕</span></span></strong>！<br />\n好好保護自己，對自己負責任！"},{"pid":"e92f037fa2a96b4c934947336c84453ae7cba97c","tid":1630314,"uid":32731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:18:49.000Z","msg":"認真po"},{"pid":"3285e847fc354520db3094d75802c73f437f838d","tid":1630314,"uid":32731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:20:54.000Z","msg":"無人理"},{"pid":"40f8283668d5a561e7b4e661d4a54e20d52d6a3f","tid":1630314,"uid":32731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:23:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e66883ef92d0afd311330643b951270972f8ceec","tid":1630314,"uid":32731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:24:29.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"7d2ef336d09ed40c0036a720a5a70ea2d16bcaeb","tid":1630314,"uid":32731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:24:39.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"76be3294baacb55bc856ae9c7957f97cf1ee05eb","tid":1630314,"uid":32731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:24:49.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"d658afe33717622282da1bcb9fb389103209bb04","tid":1630314,"uid":32731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:24:59.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"81720b7b531cd73960a40ced5b05902d6cf3b1cf","tid":1630314,"uid":32731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:25:09.000Z","msg":"5/10"},{"pid":"886a69fe7168d716d02ac41d7ef18982badce2e0","tid":1630314,"uid":32731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:25:29.000Z","msg":"6/10"},{"pid":"78fd3b98e87494909aa11df7b134f24d23aa39f8","tid":1630314,"uid":32731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:25:39.000Z","msg":"7/10"},{"pid":"c40d5c6afd45a7d9c1b777040efdcee8ab8c4135","tid":1630314,"uid":32731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:25:49.000Z","msg":"8/10"},{"pid":